    "attributes": {
        "action": "Keep May 30th as a Bank Holiday",
        "additional_details": "Most people are still under the impression that May 30th is still a bank holiday anyway so it will bring a lot of disappointment to people who have already made plans. It is also not fair on employees who now miss out on the bank holiday Monday as their employers are not allowing them to have the Friday as one instead so are now required to work.",
        "background": "I would like the government to keep the UK bank holiday May 30th 2022 as it is, as well as allowing the the Thursday and Friday as a bank holiday too.",
